    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">Machine Status Screen<draft-comment width="29px" height="13px" modified="2024-09-11" styleclass="Comment"><![CDATA[This page should be same as V180I-I1E-XD Slim3n Instruction Manual (EN) chapter 4.4]]></draft-comment></para>
