    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px;">The Machine Status Screen displays the reasons for Emergency conditions, Interlock conditions, Feed Hold conditions and machine current status.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">To navigate to Machine Status Screen, press <text style="font-weight:bold;">[MENU]</text> <text styleclass style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text> press Makino icon <text styleclass style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text> Main Menu Screen is displayed <text styleclass style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text> press Machine Status <text styleclass style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text> Machine Status Screen is displayed.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
